    <section anchor="introduction" title="Introduction">
      <t>This document contains the initial revision of the
      iana-dns-rr-types YANG module. This module defines derived types
      for the common parameters of DNS resource records: class and
      type. These types, &quot;rr-class&quot; and &quot;rr-type&quot;,
      reflect the IANA registries &quot;DNS CLASSes&quot; and
      &quot;Resource Record (RR) TYPEs&quot; <xref
      target="IANA-DNS-PARAMETERS"/>.</t>
      <t>Whenever a new class or RR type is added to the above
      registries, the iana-dns-rr-types YANG module is also updated by
      IANA.</t>
    </section>

